title: Green Rooster Farms - Rothschild Farms
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In 2016 Rothschild Farms rebranded to Green Rooster. Breakfast and lunch place with focus on local ingredients. A couple of sides are vegan as well as lunch special that is usually able to be made vegan but need to check. Makes noodle bowls where you pick the ingredients.
